Notes: I have reason to believe that the 'van Aylva' here is in reference to Cornelis van Aylva. No van Aylva with a first name that starts with G appears. It could be very well that the first name initial had been misinterpreted. It may also refer to the position of Grietman, which was held by numerous van Aylvas in Friesland, including himself. He is the only van Aylva with life dates that would best correspond to the letter we have.
